cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Changing the remote network address to an unreachable subnet IP will cause routing failure and prevent F1 interface connection to the CU.
du.explanation_zh: 將遠端網路地址更改為不可達的子網 IP 會導致路由失敗，並阻止與 CU 的 F1 介面連接。
